title: Luxurious South Lamar Apartments!
posting_body: ['Text ID # :5875A to my cell for more info!', 'BEAUTIFUL, LUXURIOUS SOUTH LAMAR APARTMENTS', 'Experience luxury living in Austin, TX at our south Lamar apartments.', 'From modern, upscale designs to a handful of convenient amenities right at your fingertips, we know your stay our apartments will be unforgettable.', 'These apartments in South Lamar offers spacious studio, one-, two-, and three-bedroom apartments.', 'Our homes are unique and creatively designed to offer comfort and convenience for residents.', 'Each home comes with necessary amenities such as a washer and dryer as well as large, spacious living areas.', 'We also offer community features such as immediate maintenance services and online bill pay to make life just a little easier.', 'The convenient location in the heart of Austin makes it easy to get around the city and enjoy the natural beauty surrounding our south Lamar apartments.', 'We have a premium location right beside the Colorado river giving you easy access to the I-35 and TX-1 Loop.', 'Visit Bullock Texas State History Museum only a few minutes away or take a stroll through Auditorium Shores at Town Lake Metropolitan Park right outside your doorstep.', 'The options are endless around our community.']
